title: PGM Map Collection
subtitle: A collection of publicly downloadable Minecraft maps made for PGM
body: This collection of maps have been specifically designed and tested to be used with the maintained PGMDev version of PGM (PvP Game Manager). ResourcePile recommends that you use the most up-to-date version of this PGM in order to have the best experience with this map. To setup your own PGM server, please follow this guide. Further PGM support can be found in the PGM Discord.

messages.message: We are currently upgrading our PGM map collection to provide access to more maps with automatic updates as soon as they are released. This redesigned collection will introduce additional information and metrics to find new maps by and bring together the various community maintained PGM map repositories in a single directory. Please leave your thoughts and feedback on the redesigned collection on our Discord.
